'''Agahungarema''' (''Chauve souris'') ni [[igikoko|agakoko]] kimeze nk'inyoni mu mababa ariko uravye neza mu maso, kameze hafi nk'umuntu. Karaguruka mu kirere ariko ntamaso gafise. Mu kwicara ku giti, karacurama umutwe ukaraba hasi. Iyo ukegereye karabimenya gakoreresheje kameremere kako. Iyo kaguruka, kigira ntikagonge ikintu, kavyumvishwa n'uko impwemu zako zikagarutseko kandi bikaba mu kanya gato cane.
